    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review use of polygraph tests in Courts",
        "additional_details": "This petition is an attempt allow polygraph tests to be used as evidence for both victim and the accused in a Court of Law. Please help me raise awareness on this subject and get this change implemented.",
        "background": "How many cases have you read about or seen on the news where years down the line after conviction they have been found innocent? Too much money is paid out in compensation today to alleged 'victims'. People suffer injustices. I demand a change. ",
